		<abstract id="abstract">
			<title>Eclipse Birt</title>
			<para> This tutorial describes how to use Eclipse BIRT for reporting
				on simple Java Objects (POJO's). The
				tutorial explains also how to deploy the resulting BIRT
				report
				into a
				webcontainer (Tomcat) and how to use it in an Eclipse
				RCP
				application. Eclipse 3.7 (Indigo) is used for this tutorial.
			</para>
		</abstract>
	</articleinfo>	
